     quite happy with the result, so that I decided to release it. The
     game should run on all Amigas.
     Now lets list up some features of Triz:

                  -fully Multitasking and `quitable` (IMPORTANT when used
                   on harddisks !!).
                  -super duper background gfx. (by me ;) )
                  -Saves a `TOP-HUNDRED` scoreboard.
                  -Shows your ranking during play.
                  -Nice but useless Histogramm.
                  -Shows your Score  (WOW, what a feature !!) ;)
                  -Nice Intro and super duper music. (be me ;) )
                  -Level Editor
                  -more blocks optionaly selectable
                  -uncrippled Shareware !!

