Why the Hell does a Game like Triz need an Editor ?? I don`t now ! But I
thought it would be nice, to be able to setup the levels according to the
players playingstrength.

O.K. To get to the Editor you have to press `e` while you are in the
Mainscreen (The Screen where the Scroller does its job). Then a window will
be opened with a lot of Buttons on it.



Installation should be very simple:
From the Workbench:
Take the Drawer `Blitztriz` and place it somewhere you want.
Copy `medplayer.library` found in `Blitztriz/libs` to LIBS:

